n, sau khi biết anh ta là ai thì công chúa không còn tin vào Nicholas nữa. Nữ hoàng Clarisse cho rằng nên mời anh ta nghỉ lại trong thời gian 30 ngày để tiện theo dõi âm mưu của ông Bá tước và người cháu trai. Kết cục câu chuyện tranh chấp ngôi vị trong hoàng gia này sẽ đi đến đâu?","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"11130","season":null,"vote_average":6.7,"vote_count":3369},"modified":"2023-06-13T12:38:13.000Z","cast":["Anne Hathaway","Julie Andrews","Héctor Elizondo","John Rhys-Davies","Heather Matarazzo","Chris Pine","Callum Blue","Larry Miller","Raven-Symoné","Kathleen Marshall","Caroline Goodall","Lorraine Nicholson","Shannon Wilcox","Greg Lewis","Abigail Breslin"],"director":["Garry Marshall"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Anne Hathaway","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Anne Hathaway","tmdb_id":1813,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s6tflSD20MGz04ZR2R1lZvhmC4Y.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1813"},{"name":"Julie Andrews","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Julie Andrews","tmdb_id":5823,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kTXM2KfsXh2vSav0s9vaDKfs4lR.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5823"},{"name":"Héctor Elizondo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Héctor Elizondo","tmdb_id":1210,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Mfx9xeOFKXtzVpAc1488LiHs0b.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1210"},{"name":"John Rhys-Davies","name_vi":null,"name_original":"John Rhys-Davies","tmdb_id":655,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qpXl1YnqQsUKYEDm3BB2zK5wbhe.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/655"},{"name":"Heather Matarazzo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Heather Matarazzo","tmdb_id":33656,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/afZhMKmsAHZA9jHq7F9tNUFZci6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/33656"},{"name":"Chris Pine","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chris Pine","tmdb_id":62064,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7mHvPL2TsfMBEeEmO0Iww8hpQXZ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb